txt.en: Supply crates can be found at Cotfast in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy supply crates at Cotfast.
Supplies found at Cotfast should be destroyed in order to lessen the strength of your foes within the Wildwood.
Supply crates can be found at Cotfast in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy supply crates at Cotfast.
Foes of the Free Peoples are keeping supplies at the village of Cotfast within the Wildwood. Destroying these supplies should lessen the strength of foes here.
